# Surge AI rule set without policy.
# Use this file as an external rule set and select the Proxy policy.
# Keep this rule set above GEOIP,CN and FINAL rules.
#
# Scope: major international generative AI websites, APIs, coding assistants,
# image/video/audio generators, and AI search/research services.
# Mainland China services such as DeepSeek, Qwen, Kimi, Doubao and Zhipu are
# intentionally excluded so they can follow your normal DIRECT rules.

